{"tid":584142,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【美股戰報】爆貿易戰憂慮加劇 道指曾挫逾300點","createTime":"2018-03-07T15:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T15:42:51.000Z","uid":174649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1110ffab6ba5760d6a0d8aa3ec4f38558fafc4d6","tid":584142,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180307/large/1520433567_7f3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180307%2Flarge%2F1520433567_7f3d.jpg&h=60ddfbce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國白宮經濟顧問主席科恩請辭，全球爆發貿易戰機會升溫，拖累美股周三早段下滑，道瓊斯工業平均指數曾挫逾300點。<br />\n<br />\n本港晚上約10時33分，道指曾跌312點，報24571點。標普500指數報2715點，跌12點。納指報7344點，跌27點。美匯指數偏軟，報89.541，跌0.09%。<br />\n歐股尾市個別發展，英國富時100指數升0.2%、德國DAX指數升0.59%，法國CAC指數跌0.13%。追蹤整體歐洲股市表現Stoxx 600指數升0.01%。"},{"pid":"8789f26d73abb56a7ae3cac70563050f3d9ccda4","tid":584142,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"過兩日就消化到"},{"pid":"9dd8781d8be50e4d898b3da5630532948fd03841","tid":584142,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbfa1dfd34121a578a664fabe0720704a6dbe3a5","tid":584142,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd8781d8be50e4d898b3da5630532948fd03841","tid":584142,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8789f26d73abb56a7ae3cac70563050f3d9ccda4","tid":584142,"uid":42751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:20:53.000Z","msg":"過兩日就消化到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"唔洗兩日 過多兩個鐘就倒升"},{"pid":"125c3a9f0ac2c3cb83636b45f0ab7b6925e0a389","tid":584142,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dd8781d8be50e4d898b3da5630532948fd03841","tid":584142,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s